---
title: Comforting Bacon, Feta & Potato Pie with Filo Pastry & Roasted Broccoli
description: This cosy dinner packs in a veggie-loaded bacon base that's full of flavour, especially when it's packed with goodies like
roasted broccoli and feta. Be sure to serve it fresh from the oven for that beloved cosy pie experience!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
